RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO,USER_REF_NO,PRODUCT_CODE,COUNTERPARTY FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT WHERE MODULE_CODE ='OL' AND CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'L') AND BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND PRODUCT_TYPE <> 'C' ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO
SELECT A.STATUS, B.DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER A, OLTMS_CONTRACT_STATUSES B WHERE A.PRODUCT =? AND A.STATUS =B.STATUS_CODE AND B.STATUS_TYPE = 'C'ORDER BY A.STATUS_SEQUENCE
SELECT A.STATUS, B.DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER A, OLTMS_CONTRACT_STATUSES B WHERE A.PRODUCT = ? AND A.STATUS = B.STATUS_CODE AND B.STATUS_TYPE = 'C' ORDER BY A.STATUS_SEQUENCE

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_SUMMARY_WHERECLAUSE: exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id) AND MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND PRODUCT_TYPE <> 'C'
RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND PRODUCT_TYPE <> 'C' and Branch IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID) and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = PRODUCT_CODE AND USER_ID = global.user_id)
